name                oinkmaster
version             2.0
revision            1
categories          net
license             BSD
maintainers         gmail.com:mschamschula openmaintainer
description         Oinkmaster is a script that will help you update and manage your \
                    Snort rules.
long_description    {*}${description}
platforms           darwin
homepage            http://oinkmaster.sourceforge.net/
